Last updated: January 2026

SoundFocus respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how information is handled when you use the SoundFocus app.

⸻

1. Personal Data Collection

SoundFocus does not require account creation and does not directly collect personal information such as name, email address, or phone number.

All focus sessions, statistics, and preferences entered by the user are stored locally on the device.

⸻

2. Internet Connection

SoundFocus can function offline for core features such as focus sessions and statistics.

However, an internet connection may be required for:
	•	Displaying advertisements
	•	Processing in-app purchases
	•	Loading third-party services related to ads

⸻

3. Local Data Storage

All user-generated data including:
	•	Completed focus sessions
	•	Total focus time
	•	Focus statistics

is stored only on the user’s device using local storage.

This data is not uploaded to our servers.

⸻

4. Advertising & Third-Party Services

SoundFocus displays banner and interstitial advertisements using Google AdMob, a third-party advertising service.

Google AdMob may automatically collect certain device-level information, including:
	•	Device identifiers (such as advertising identifiers)
	•	Advertising interaction data
	•	Approximate usage data related to ads

This data may be used by Google to:
	•	Display relevant advertisements
	•	Measure ad performance
	•	Prevent fraud and abuse

SoundFocus does not have access to or control over the data collected by Google AdMob.

Users can permanently remove all advertisements by purchasing the “Remove Ads” one-time in-app purchase.

⸻

5. In-App Purchases

SoundFocus offers a one-time, non-consumable in-app purchase that removes advertisements permanently.

Purchase processing is handled securely by Apple. SoundFocus does not collect or store any payment information.

⸻

6. App Tracking Transparency

SoundFocus complies with Apple’s App Tracking Transparency (ATT) framework.

When required, users are asked for permission before tracking-related data is accessed. Tracking preferences can be managed at any time through iOS system settings.

⸻

7. Data Sharing

SoundFocus does not sell or trade user data.

Limited data may be processed by third-party services (such as Google AdMob) solely for advertising and measurement purposes, in accordance with their privacy policies.

⸻

8. Children’s Privacy

SoundFocus does not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13.

If you believe a child has provided personal information, please contact us so appropriate action can be taken.

⸻

9. Data Security

All user-generated data is stored locally on the device.

Reasonable technical measures are implemented to protect the app and its data.

⸻

10. Changes to This Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time.
Any changes will be reflected within the app or on the App Store product page.

⸻

11. Contact

If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

Email: 6353ww@gmail.com
